<ref name=Gaddis_2014/><ref name=Sharp_1977/>，它大约形成于[[雨海|雨海]]之前或稍后一些<ref name=North_2007>{{cite book     
 |title      = Observing the Moon
 |author     = North G.
 |date       = 2007
 |publisher  = Cambridge University Press
